<section xml:id="ch2-section-figure-sources" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Figure sources</title>

    <p>
        <ol>
            <li xml:id="ch2-eclipse-figure-source">
                <title>Great North American Eclipse</title>
                <p>
                    This image originally appeared in the NASA Earth Observatory story <url href="https://science.nasa.gov/earth/earth-observatory/total-solar-eclipse-darkens-north-america-152663/"><articletitle>Total Solar Eclipse Darkens North America</articletitle></url>.
                    NASA Earth Observatory image by <url href="https://science.nasa.gov/earth/earth-observatory/about-the-eo/">Michala Garrison and Wanmei Liang</url>,
                    using data from <url href="https://epic.gsfc.nasa.gov/">DSCOVR EPIC</url> and VIIRS data from NASA EOSDIS <url href="https://www.earthdata.nasa.gov/data/projects/lance">LANCE</url>,
                    <url href="https://worldview.earthdata.nasa.gov/">GIBS/Worldview</url>,
                    and the <url href="https://www.nesdis.noaa.gov/our-satellites/currently-flying/joint-polar-satellite-system">Joint Polar Satellite System</url> (JPSS).
                    Story by <url href="https://science.nasa.gov/earth/earth-observatory/about-the-eo/">Emily Cassidy</url>.
                    Licensed under <url href="https://www.nasa.gov/nasa-brand-center/images-and-media/">NASA Images and Media Usage Guidelines</url>.
                    Accessed via <url href="https://science.nasa.gov/earth/earth-observatory/total-solar-eclipse-darkens-north-america-152663/">NASA Earth Observatory</url>.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </p>
